@{U}4.12 The command line dialogue                                TeraDesk@{u}  
  
When  a  TTP-type  or GTP-type program (see Types of program files) is 
activated  by  clicking  on  its  name or icon, or through the Open... 
menu,  a  dialogue  box  will  appear  through which it is possible to 
enter  the  required  parameters.  If  the  program  is  activated  by 
dragging  a  file  onto  the  program  name or icon, this box will not 
